metadata.name: Distraction In Abstraction #1
metadata.description:
Series 1 of 3 the first 100 get a Wl spot for the next set released. First two series will have 475 and the final series will have 1000. Next set Release Date 12/10.

The world is a beautiful place. So full of color, and life. And what's more, it's all made up of geometric abstract shapes. God looks down upon the world, and sees nothing but perfection. Each shape is placed perfectly in relation to the others, forming a harmonious whole.
